mb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/6/4/BB26_NCAASuperRegSoldOut_1920x1080.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Thu, 4 Jun 2026 09:59:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59163</s:story_id></item><item><title>Limited Amount of NCAA Morgantown Super Regional Tickets Now Available</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/6/4/baseball-limited-amount-of-ncaa-morgantown-super-regional-tickets-now-available</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/6/4/baseball-limited-amount-of-ncaa-morgantown-super-regional-tickets-now-available</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Supers Tickets On Sale" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/6/4/BB26_NCAARegTixOnSale_1920x1080.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. - The Mountaineers will host the NCAA Morgantown Super Regional at Kendrick Family Ballpark this Friday, June 5 through Sunday, June 7.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/6/4/BB26_NCAARegTixOnSale_1920x1080.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/6/4/BB26_NCAARegTixOnSale_1920x1080.jpg"><media:title>Supers Tickets On Sale</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/6/4/BB26_NCAARegTixOnSale_1920x1080.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Thu, 4 Jun 2026 09:58:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59164</s:story_id></item><item><title>West Virginia Set to Host NCAA Super Regionals</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/6/2/baseball-west-virginia-set-to-host-ncaa-super-regionals</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/6/2/baseball-west-virginia-set-to-host-ncaa-super-regionals</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="WVU baseball players sing Country Roads after winning the NCAA Morgantown Regional." src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/6/2/WVU_V_UK_Monday-127.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – The West Virginia University baseball team will host the NCAA Super Regionals against Cal Poly from June 5-7. First pitch on Friday and Saturday is scheduled for 12 p.m. on both days with Sunday's game time to be determined. It is a best-of-three format with Sunday's game only being played if needed.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/6/2/WVU_V_UK_Monday-127.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/6/2/WVU_V_UK_Monday-127.jpg"><media:title>WVU baseball players sing Country Roads after winning the NCAA Morgantown Regional.</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/6/2/WVU_V_UK_Monday-127.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Tue, 2 Jun 2026 12:55:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59159</s:story_id></item><item><title>West Virginia Claims Morgantown Regional Title</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/6/2/baseball-west-virginia-claims-morgantown-regional-title</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/6/2/baseball-west-virginia-claims-morgantown-regional-title</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="The West Virginia baseball team poses for a photo after winning the Morgantown Regional" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/6/2/060126_BSB_Kentucky_NCAAT_GB-11.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – For the third consecutive season, the West Virginia University baseball team advanced to the NCAA Super Regionals as the Mountaineers defeated Kentucky, 6-5, in 10 innings, Monday evening at Kendrick Family Ballpark to win the Morgantown Regional.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/6/2/060126_BSB_Kentucky_NCAAT_GB-11.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/6/2/060126_BSB_Kentucky_NCAAT_GB-11.jpg"><media:title>The West Virginia baseball team poses for a photo after winning the Morgantown Regional</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/6/2/060126_BSB_Kentucky_NCAAT_GB-11.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Tue, 2 Jun 2026 00:49:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59156</s:story_id></item><item><title>Baseball Fans, Savor These Special Moments</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/6/2/baseball-fans-savor-these-special-moments</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/6/2/baseball-fans-savor-these-special-moments</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="West Virginia fans celebrate the Mountaineers' walk-off, 6-5 victory over Kentucky in the deciding game of the Morgantown Regional played at Kendrick Family Ballpark on Monday, June 1, 2026." src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/6/2/Celebration-Main.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – I'm old, and watching college baseball games these last couple of days has made me feel much older.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/6/2/Celebration-Main.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/6/2/Celebration-Main.jpg"><media:title>West Virginia fans celebrate the Mountaineers' walk-off, 6-5 victory over Kentucky in the deciding game of the Morgantown Regional played at Kendrick Family Ballpark on Monday, June 1, 2026.</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/6/2/Celebration-Main.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Tue, 2 Jun 2026 08:58:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59157</s:story_id></item><item><title>Bridgeport’s McDougal Seizes Opportunity to Extend West Virginia’s Season</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/6/1/baseball-bridgeports-mcdougal-seizes-opportunity-to-extend-west-virginias-season</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/6/1/baseball-bridgeports-mcdougal-seizes-opportunity-to-extend-west-virginias-season</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="West Virginia players celebrate winning pitcher Ben McDougal's five-inning relief stint in the Mountaineers' 11-9 victory over Kentucky to set up a deciding game five on Monday at Kendrick Family Ballpark in Morgantown, W.Va." src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/6/1/McDougal2-Main.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – During a long, 12-hour day when West Virginia pounded out 23 hits and 21 runs in victories over Wake Forest and Kentucky, you knew for the Mountaineers to keep their postseason hopes alive, somebody in a gold-colored jersey was going to have to man-up on the pitching mound.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/6/1/McDougal2-Main.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/6/1/McDougal2-Main.jpg"><media:title>West Virginia players celebrate winning pitcher Ben McDougal's five-inning relief stint in the Mountaineers' 11-9 victory over Kentucky to set up a deciding game five on Monday at Kendrick Family Ballpark in Morgantown, W.Va.</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/6/1/McDougal2-Main.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Mon, 1 Jun 2026 00:32:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59153</s:story_id></item><item><title>WVU Athletics Names The Goat WV Pub the Official Sports Pub of the Mountaineers</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/6/2/general-wvu-athletics-names-the-goat-wv-pub-the-official-sports-pub-of-the-mountaineers</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/6/2/general-wvu-athletics-names-the-goat-wv-pub-the-official-sports-pub-of-the-mountaineers</guid><category>General</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="The GOAT has been Named the Official Sports Pub of WVU Athletics" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/6/2/WVU_x_The_Goat__3_.png" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W. Va. – West Virginia Athletics and Mountaineer Sports Properties announced today a five-year partnership extension with The Goat WV Pub that includes the creation a new Gold & Blue NIL Show.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/6/2/WVU_x_The_Goat__3_.png" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/6/2/WVU_x_The_Goat__3_.png"><media:title>The GOAT has been Named the Official Sports Pub of WVU Athletics</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/6/2/WVU_x_The_Goat__3_.png" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Tue, 2 Jun 2026 13:00:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>3</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59158</s:story_id></item></channel></rss>